---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Terms & Conditions" description="Terms and Conditions for J&N Junk Removal services in Long Island, NY.">

  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="page-hero-bg"></div>
    <div class="container page-hero-content">
      <p class="section-label">Legal</p>
      <h1 class="section-title light">TERMS & CONDITIONS</h1>
      <p class="page-hero-sub">Last updated: May 19, 2026</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="legal-main">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="legal-content">

        <h2>1. Agreement to Terms</h2>
        <p>By accessing our website <strong>jandnjunkremoval.com</strong> or using our services, you agree to be bound by these Terms and Conditions. If you do not agree, please do not use our website or services.</p>

        <h2>2. Services</h2>
        <p>J&N Junk Removal provides junk removal, hauling, and cleanup services in Long Island, NY and surrounding areas. All services are subject to availability and scheduling confirmation by our team.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Service appointments are confirmed via phone or email after form submission</li>
          <li>Same-day service is subject to availability</li>
          <li>We reserve the right to refuse service for items we cannot legally or safely remove</li>
          <li>Final pricing is confirmed before work begins — no hidden fees</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>3. Booking & Scheduling</h2>
        <p>Submitting our online booking form does not guarantee a confirmed appointment. Our team will contact you to confirm the date, time, and pricing before your scheduled pickup. Appointments are finalized upon verbal or written confirmation from J&N Junk Removal.</p>

        <h2>4. Payment</h2>
        <p>Payment is due upon completion of services unless otherwise agreed in writing. We accept cash and major payment methods. No payment is required to submit a booking request online.</p>

        <h2>5. SMS Communications</h2>
        <p>By checking the SMS consent box on our contact form, you agree to receive text messages from J&N Junk Removal at the number provided, including:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Booking confirmations and reminders</li>
          <li>Appointment updates and scheduling changes</li>
          <li>Service-related notifications</li>
        </ul>
        <p>Message and data rates may apply. Message frequency varies. Reply <strong>STOP</strong> to unsubscribe at any time. Reply <strong>HELP</strong> for assistance. Opting out of SMS will not affect your booking or service.</p>

        <h2>6. Cancellations</h2>
        <p>We ask that you notify us at least 2 hours before your scheduled pickup if you need to cancel or reschedule. You can reach us at <strong>(516) 981-3365</strong> or <strong>jnjunkremovalservices@gmail.com</strong>.</p>

        <h2>7. Liability</h2>
        <p>J&N Junk Removal will take reasonable care when removing items from your property. We are not liable for:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Pre-existing damage to property</li>
          <li>Items not disclosed at the time of booking</li>
          <li>Damage resulting from access limitations or hazardous conditions not communicated in advance</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>8. Prohibited Items</h2>
        <p>We do not remove hazardous materials including but not limited to: asbestos, chemicals, biohazardous waste, propane tanks, or any items prohibited by local, state, or federal regulations.</p>

        <h2>9. Intellectual Property</h2>
        <p>All content on this website including text, images, and logos is the property of J&N Junk Removal and may not be reproduced without written permission.</p>

        <h2>10. Governing Law</h2>
        <p>These Terms are governed by the laws of the State of New York. Any disputes shall be resolved in the courts of Nassau County, New York.</p>

        <h2>11. Changes to Terms</h2>
        <p>We reserve the right to update these Terms at any time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated date. Continued use of our services after changes constitutes acceptance.</p>

        <h2>12. Contact Us</h2>
        <p>Questions about these Terms? Contact us:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Email:</strong> jnjunkremovalservices@gmail.com</li>
          <li><strong>Phone:</strong> (516) 981-3365</li>
          <li><strong>Address:</strong> Valley Stream, NY 11580</li>
        </ul>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  .page-hero { background: var(--black); padding: 80px 0 72px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
  .page-hero-bg { position: absolute; inset: 0; background: radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 100% at 100% 50%, rgba(211,47,47,0.1) 0%, transparent 70%); }
  .page-hero-content { position: relative; z-index: 1; }
  .page-hero-sub { color: #888; font-size: 1rem; margin-top: 16px; }

  .legal-main { padding: 80px 0; background: var(--gray-light); }
  .legal-content { background: var(--white); padding: 48px 40px; box-shadow: 0 4px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.07); max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .legal-content h2 { font-family: var(--font-condensed); font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 1px; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--black); margin: 32px 0 12px; padding-bottom: 8px; border-bottom: 2px solid var(--red); }
  .legal-content h2:first-child { margin-top: 0; }
  .legal-content p { font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--gray-text); line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .legal-content ul { margin: 0 0 16px 20px; }
  .legal-content ul li { font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--gray-text); line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .legal-content strong { color: var(--black); }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .legal-content { padding: 32px 20px; }
  }
</style>
